        <mxCell id="IG7Cz-LUzywHiOBToCAp-5" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;design an e- commerce system with following requirements:&lt;br&gt;1. user login service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. search service&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. product catalog service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. cart service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5. order status service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;6. check out service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;optimize the product searching and inventory stock management in real time&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="460" x="20" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IG7Cz-LUzywHiOBToCAp-10" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Functional requirements:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;1) user should be able to log in&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;2) user should be able to access and search the catalog&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;3) user should be able to add items to cart&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;4) user should be able to check the status of their order&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;5) user should be able to check out the cart&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;non-functional requirements:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;1) system should be able to handle 1.5 millionn daily active users&lt;br&gt;2) systen should be able to optimize the following in real time:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; - product searching&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; - inventory stock management&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;3) latency: 300ms at most&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="470" x="20" y="340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
